            <p eId="annex_1_p_9"><b>Subject matter and legislative competence of devolved legislatures</b></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>19 </num>
              <p>This Act amends sections 12(2) and 36 of the 2018 Act which extend to England and Wales, Scotland and Northern Ireland. The subject matter of those provisions is not devolved to the legislatures in Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland.</p>
            </blockContainer>
